Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Die Buchtitel von Rubens"

  • Draft text "Anmerkungen" (footnotes)
  • Extracts from different publications about engraved title pages
  • Correspondence with the director of the Deutsches Buchmuseum (Leipzig)
  • Subfolder (Annotation: "Rubens Bücher von Moretus bezogen. (Nach Rooses)" addressed to "Herrn Dr. Hans Gerhard Evers München 23 Simmernstr. 8/0" and dated 13.02.1939):
    • Munich university library filled forms
    • Extracts from different publications and sketches
  • Photos of engraved pages with notes and sketches
